# fastembed runtime cache — created when tests/dev runs download
# ONNX model weights (~80 MB). Must NEVER be packaged into a crate;
# QF-2026-06-02-09 in the workspace quality backlog was caused by
# this exact dir leaking into `cargo package`.
.fastembed_cache/
**/.fastembed_cache/
